# Exclude redundant/legacy API routes so we stay within Vercel Hobby's
# 12-serverless-function limit. All their functionality is consolidated into
# api/data.js, api/auth.js and api/payment.js, and the frontend's apiShim
# transparently rewrites old paths to these. Do NOT ship these as functions.

